> **Источник:** [ui-ux-pro-max](https://github.com/nextlevelbuilder/ui-ux-pro-max-skill) v2.5
> **Кто читает:** feature-developer (IMPL), ux-expert (QUALITY_GATE), qa-expert (QA), code-simplifier (SIMPLIFY)
