## Pre-Delivery Checklist

> **feature-developer:** проверь перед AGENT_REPORT.
> **ux-expert:** используй как дополнение к design-audit checklist.

### Visual Quality
- [ ] No emojis used as icons (use SVG instead)
- [ ] All icons from a consistent icon family and style
- [ ] cursor-pointer on all clickable elements
- [ ] Hover states with smooth transitions (150-300ms)
- [ ] Semantic theme tokens used consistently (no ad-hoc hardcoded colors)

### Interaction
- [ ] All interactive elements provide clear hover/focus/press feedback
- [ ] Touch targets meet minimum size (>= 44x44pt)
- [ ] Disabled states are visually clear and non-interactive
- [ ] Loading states show spinner/skeleton for async operations

### Contrast & Theming
- [ ] Primary text contrast >= 4.5:1 in both light and dark mode
- [ ] Secondary text contrast >= 3:1 in both light and dark mode
- [ ] Dividers/borders visible in both modes

### Layout
- [ ] Responsive: tested at 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- [ ] No horizontal scroll on mobile
- [ ] 4/8px spacing rhythm maintained
- [ ] Content does not collide with fixed headers/footers

### Accessibility
- [ ] Focus states visible for keyboard navigation
- [ ] prefers-reduced-motion respected
- [ ] All meaningful images/icons have alt text or aria-label
- [ ] Color is not the only indicator (add icon/text)
- [ ] Heading hierarchy is sequential (no level skip)

### Performance
- [ ] Images use lazy loading (below-the-fold)
- [ ] No layout shift from async content (skeleton/reserved space)
- [ ] Lists with 50+ items are virtualized
